						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of 45 sheep for maintaining half a perpetual lamp before the image of <hi rend="bold">Ādittagaram-Uḍaiyār (Sūrya)</hi> by a shepherd named Tāyaṉ Śāttaṉ of of Innambar, ‘by the gracious order of Tiruppuṟambiyam-Uḍaiyār’. </p>						

